import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib inline

import seaborn as sns

x = np.linspace(0, 14, 100)
y1 = np.sin(x)
y2 = 2*np.sin(x+0.5)
y3 = 3*np.sin(x+1.0)
y4 = 4*np.sin(x+1.5)

plt.figure(figsize=(10,6))
plt.plot(x,y1, x,y2, x,y3, x,y4)
plt.show()
